

The server can be run using something like:

OPENMAPI_TARGET_HOST=127.0.0.1:7000 OPENMAPI_CERT_FILE=ca.cer OPENMAPI_KEY_FILE=ca.key mono --debug bin/nmapisvr.exe

SSL-certificates are required.



